<br>
yea Pull with slow, haste pet, rune yourself incase, keep Charm up since you can charm HGs and its the best tool you got to excape, oh keep sow up all times most druids are very happy to SoW for Clarity and will often come back to you or call you for group. ask clerics for buffs for a Clarity, we will often be happy to oblige, try and get a simble of them some wont give you the lvl 44 one but its almost 20 plat a componet to me so i cant blame them, but my Cha is horred (45).<br>
<br>
Best team is 44+ cleric and 44+ enchanter + pet and a Sharman Druid or Ranger for sows, I perfer shammy because of there buffs slows and dots. and thay have an additional pet for use.<br>
<br>
Cleric gets sow and Pulls since thay will probly have the best AC and HP unless there a High elf then its normaly about equal.  keep the pets hasted, and cleric buffs on them, if the cleric dont make them crease a /target Goober or whatever the pets names are so he can keep them healed.<br>
<br>
that combo you can do HGs easly.<br>
